---
title: Dukkah-Roasted Cauliflower & Freekeh Salad with Garlic Yoghurt
description: This delightful dish is a celebration of wholesome roasted veggies with freekeh and fragrant mint. Add dukkah and roasted almonds for extra flavour and crunch, then top it off with a drizzle of garlicky yoghurt.
